00:46:09,513 --> 00:46:13,302
<font color="yellow">I already watched this movie. It's really fun!</font>

658
00:46:13,327 --> 00:46:15,330
<font color="yellow">Really? I'm looking forward to it!</font>

659
00:46:15,419 --> 00:46:19,825
<font color="yellow">- Mr. Jo, can I have two tickets for my children?
