00:47:25,198 --> 00:47:27,135
<font color="yellow">No, I didn't suffer at all.</font>

672
00:47:29,378 --> 00:47:32,917
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong couldn't even take
a break. On top of that, she had to</font>

673
00:47:33,137 --> 00:47:36,373
<font color="yellow">go back and forth from work.
