00:47:38,886 --> 00:47:40,760
<font color="yellow">gave their daughters-in-law such a rough time.</font>

676
00:47:40,785 --> 00:47:41,940
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

677
00:47:42,722 --> 00:47:46,870
<font color="yellow">No, it's fine. I wasn't complaining to you.</font>

678
00:47:48,768 --> 00:47:51,354
<font color="yellow">You have to walk on eggshells around
