679
00:47:51,379 --> 00:47:54,097
<font color="yellow">You must be having
a hard time in the middle.</font>

680
00:47:55,800 --> 00:47:59,584
<font color="yellow">I'm just hoping time will solve everything.</font>

681
00:48:03,800 --> 00:48:06,426
<font color="yellow">Mother, take this.</font>

682
00:48:08,932 --> 00:48:10,596
<font color="yellow">What's this?</font>

683
00:48:11,120 --> 00:48:14,714
<font color="yellow">It's a coat.
