684
00:48:15,230 --> 00:48:18,549
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear! No, I'm fine!</font>

685
00:48:19,519 --> 00:48:22,792
<font color="yellow">Oh my goodness. This looks expensive.</font>

686
00:48:23,315 --> 00:48:25,969
<font color="yellow">I can do this much for you as your son-in-law.</font>

687
00:48:26,534 --> 00:48:28,018
<font color="yellow">Mother, try it on.</font>

688
00:48:29,690 --> 00:48:30,690
<font color="yellow">Oh, all right.</font>

689
00:48:31,659 --> 00:48:33,276
<font color="yellow">Oh, my. Look at the color!</font>

690
00:48:33,744 --> 00:48:34,744
<font color="yellow">It's so pretty!</font>

691
00:48:36,948 --> 00:48:37,948
<font color="yellow">Wow!</font>

692
00:48:39,355 --> 00:48:40,355
<font color="yellow">Wow! Amazing!</font>

693
00:48:40,830 --> 00:48:42,630
<font color="yellow">You look beautiful, grandma!</font>

694
00:48:43,448 --> 00:48:45,124
<font color="yellow">- Right, Yoo-sung?
- Yes!</font>

695
00:48:45,149 --> 00:48:47,048
<font color="yellow">- It looks good on her, right?
- Yes!</font>

696
00:48:50,369 --> 00:48:51,369
<font color="yellow">It's warm.</font>

697
00:48:58,392 --> 00:48:59,392
<font color="yellow">Jang-go.</font>

698
00:49:00,845 --> 00:49:01,845
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

699
00:49:02,142 --> 00:49:05,212
<font color="yellow">I was hungry, so I was looking
