719
00:50:07,285 --> 00:50:09,448
<font color="yellow">I bought one for her last year. It's fine.</font>

720
00:50:09,473 --> 00:50:12,079
<font color="yellow">That was last year, and this is this year!</font>

721
00:50:12,104 --> 00:50:13,171
<font color="yellow">Hurry up and go.</font>

722
00:50:24,831 --> 00:50:26,304
<font color="yellow">What do we do?</font>

723
00:50:35,994 --> 00:50:38,981
<font color="yellow">How could he only buy
a coat for his mother-in-law?</font>

724
00:50:40,237 --> 00:50:41,525
<font color="yellow">Oh my gosh.</font>

725
00:50:44,088 --> 00:50:46,088
<font color="yellow">Mom, what are you doing?</font>

