00:50:47,127 --> 00:50:49,064
<font color="yellow">Can't you tell? I'm wiping the floor.</font>

727
00:50:51,127 --> 00:50:52,327
<font color="yellow">Mom, let's go out.</font>

728
00:50:53,057 --> 00:50:54,057
<font color="yellow">Go where?</font>

729
00:50:54,611 --> 00:50:57,447
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong said we should buy you a coat.</font>

730
00:50:58,979 --> 00:51:01,187
<font color="yellow">You don't have to buy it for me, so get out.</font>

731
00:51:02,401 --> 00:51:04,224
<font color="yellow">Really? You don't need a coat?</font>

732
00:51:05,119 --> 00:51:07,525
<font color="yellow">I told you that you don't
