733
00:51:08,635 --> 00:51:10,532
<font color="yellow">Why are you getting mad? Okay then.</font>

734
00:51:14,651 --> 00:51:17,752
<font color="yellow">Oh my god! He's really leaving? That jerk!</font>

735
00:51:19,510 --> 00:51:24,245
<font color="yellow">This is why they say it's no use having a son!</font>

736
00:51:24,837 --> 00:51:28,543
<font color="yellow">Oh my god! That jerk!</font>

737
00:51:29,893 --> 00:51:31,884
<font color="yellow">- Thank you.
- Thank you.</font>

738
00:51:31,909 --> 00:51:34,553
<font color="yellow">- Please spread the news about us.
